Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Everyone must have someone\Nwhom they want to kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\clip(1342,738,1342,738)\fscx346\fscy397}l think what he said started it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}We wrote the names of the people\Nwe want to kill as a kind of joke,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}and showed each other secretly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Takafumi Kono{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}But maybe, someone\Ndidn't think that it was joke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do you suspect me?\Nl'll tell you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}the name l wrote\Nwas Yutaro Yamagiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Fujii, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The unidentified body found\Nin a mountain in Kanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}was Dr Yutaro Yamagiwa,\Ncommonly known as Dr Yamagiwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Several unbelievable incidents\Nhappened right under my nose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}They couldn't find his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Even at somewhere l don't know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Something started to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Fujii, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Somehow your face looks\Neven weirder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Could you have found\NDr Yamagiwa's head in your flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, l did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, l didn't! lt isn't in my flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}My flat is totally empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Anyway, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's say, in the unlikely case\Nthat the head is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}if it is so obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}then the murderer can't be me,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You must be the murderer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You don't normally have\Nsomeone's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Yutaro Yamagiwa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Someone killed the person\Nthat you want dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}you have to kill someone's too,\Nor you'll violate the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Obey the rules properly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Your Turn to Kill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Will you throw away the rubbish,\Nplease?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You know, Yutaro Yamagiwa\Ndidn't just have his head removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it seems that his fingerprints\Nwere burned too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Orangutan Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Shota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It appears that the murderer\Nhid the dead body's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}to delay the process\Nof the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}In other words,\Nthe murder was planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The murderer bore a deep grudge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and swore to kill him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}They had imagined how to kill\NYamagiwa and deceive the police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How is my suspicion?\Nls it a bull's-eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Stop thinking about that\Nand go to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But you've been thinking a lot\Nlately too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}And you're absent minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What? Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Because that's my toothbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why? Do you think it's gross?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- No, l...\N- Do you not love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I do, but using another person's\Ntoothbrush is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But l can use yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Don't use it!\N- Just occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, loving someone and this,\Nare different matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}To me, loving someone is being able\Nto use the same toothbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I've actually used yours many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You know?\NBut you look so depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The property manager\Nsuddenly died and l...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l'm sorry that giving you a hug\Nis all l can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It's okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You don't look okay, so l'll hug you\Nfor ten more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Whose stomach just rumbled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You don't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I want to stay so close to you that\Nl can't tell whose stomach rumbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I won't hide anything from you.\Nl swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Premium Contemporary{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Dr Yamagiwa's Murder{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Dr Yamagiwa\NWhere is his head?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Excuse me.\N- Whoa, chai, chai, chai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, it's you, Miss Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Did you say\N"Whoa, chai, chai, chai?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l was startled. l couldn't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What does\N"Whoa, chai, chai, chai" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It doesn't mean anything.\Nl shouted because you startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I startled you,\Nso you carelessly cursed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I didn't curse you!\NWhat are you doing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I was made to clean\Nthe rubbish collection area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Did you sort it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'll curse you if you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Hello.\N- Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Which floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You won't get off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, yes, l will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Hang on.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Will you be available tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sora, do you have to go\Nto nursery school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What about the live programme?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We can't do it without a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Hey...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If you want to say something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}say it when the kid isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If you shout at his mother\Nin front of him, it'll hurt him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay. Yes, you can bring that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hurry up! Or l'll beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come on, he'll beat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'll take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, someone might be able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You two are always so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Not exactly, l just always\Nrely on her to look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- That's not the case.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No need to be modest.\NYou really help me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, by the way, Misato,\Nshow the lady that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- "That"?\N- Yes, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What l asked you to keep for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You know what she refers to just by\Nthat? You two are really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Are you okay?\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- I'm okay...\N- Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Sachiko...\N- l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You don't have to tell Goro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}or he will be angry at you that you\Nforgot to lock the wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How kind of you to cover it up\Nfor your daughter-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I should learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}lt is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Dr Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Will you tell me when you come in?\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What else? l'm here to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course. l am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You haven't been yourself lately.\Nl am worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sorry. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You see, your reputation is very bad\Namong the patients and nurses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}so l am worried\Nthat you will be fired soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm saying that if l complain\Nabout you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}even if it's something trivial,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}you'll be fired at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That's how much your job is at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}So don't you dare\Ncause me any problems, Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Answer me!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I look forward to working with you\Ntoday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What do you think about Mr Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I mean, Mr Fujii...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Someone said\Nthat maybe he killed Dr Yamagiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Almost everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't think he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}At that time, Mr Fujii...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The unidentified dead body has been\Nfound to be Dr Yutaro Yamagiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}He was shocked and it seems\Nthat he really had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}He couldn't have killed the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The deaths of the property manager\Nand Yutaro Yamagiwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}have nothing to do\Nwith the game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do you find anyone\Namong the residents suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't want them dead, but there\Nis someone l hope will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The person l want to kill\Nand l don't know everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I wanted him to die once,\Ncome back to life, then die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why don't we reveal it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do not show anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Now, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Kojima Kids' English Class{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Thank you for teaching me.\NSee you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}See you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Has everyone got biscuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Come to my home!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Kazu, you haven't been coming\Nto my lessons lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mummy told us to say\Nthat we had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}"I'll attend the urgent\Nresidents' meeting. Nana."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}My point is,\Nthe rumour is groundless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}let's not hurt Mr Fujii's feelings\Nbecause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}And my point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}don't call us to meet\Njust for something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It isn't trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You have no right\Nto summon us to a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I do. lt is written on the contract\Nwe signed when we moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If something makes\Nthe residents suffer any harm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- You know...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I love seeing middle-aged men\Ngetting desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The contract is about water leakage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The person concerned, Mr Fujii,\Nis absent in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Everyone, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Our property manager\Nand Yutaro Yamagiwa died,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it's made all of us worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Because they could've been\Nkilled by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why? Mrs lshizaki, do you think\Nsomeone among us killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No! l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Because some people are absent\Nfrom the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't want to get suspicious\Nlike this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Please be careful of what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You are being too serious as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Ukita, you always say\Nthat l am a serious person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}but l am not that serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I may not look it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}but l joined a theatre group called\NHumour Estate when l was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Like The Third Stage in the East,\NSotobakomachi in the West,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Minami Banzai lchiza
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and Gekidan Shinkansen,\Nit was full of humour...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That's why l say you're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't suspect anyone of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}but Mr Fujii has been\Nreceiving threatening notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Threatening notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Lately, l find these every day\Nwhen l go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Murder lnducement{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What is this? Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}lt is murder inducement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}A person who induces another\Nto commit a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}shall be dealt with in\Nsentencing as a principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}ln other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}lnducement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It means incite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Even if you didn't carry it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}if you incite or urge someone\Nto murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}you'll be punished,\Nlike the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You know a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You copied those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I didn't. lt's mentioned\Nin detective stories occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Who sent them to Mr Fujii and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If they were sent by the person\Nwho killed Yutaro Yamagiwa,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l think they mean,\Nhe is just as guilty as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If you say that, everyone\Nwho participated in the game
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}induced someone\Nto commit murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why do you have this conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If writing who we want to kill\Nmakes us guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}then we're all guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But l just wrote a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I was forced to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That's why l said it was absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But that's what the law is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Even though you had no idea\Nand had no such intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it is still a crime\Nand you will be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But it's quite funny\Nif we'll all be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}In the end,\Nwho sent them to Mr Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Someone among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Stop looking at each other\Nwith suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}First of all, everybody here\Ndidn't kill Yutaro Yamagiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That means it was someone\Nwho is absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}For example, the Chinese girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}or the workaholic woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}or the S&M university student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}S&M university student?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You know, the girl in Room 202.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}She always has bandage\Non a part of her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The same thing turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't get the wrong idea.\Nl am an extreme masochist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What did we get wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This isn't a place for you to\Ntalk about something so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You had never fought with anyone\Neven when you worked at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l didn't have a fight.\Nl only slammed the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Go and find something new
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}to be enthusiastic about,\Nlike when you used to have a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't say it like l'm an old man\Nretired from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Recruiting theatre group members{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Since we became friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}we've only been talking\Nabout murderers and victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and it's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I want to hear you brag\Nabout your new married life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}There is nothing\Nworth talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You look like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Hello.\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- I think we shouldn't ask.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You're joking. Really? ls it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}So in the end,\Nwhat did you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- What do you mean?\N- The residents' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why did you have an urgent meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Are you going to lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Nana, you have a habit\Nto bite your lip when you lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why do you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You lied about me biting my lip,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You always scratch\Nyour right chest when you lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Actually, l have used it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Nana, you have a habit\Nto bite your lip when you lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What? l'm not aware of it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- You often do it.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}So, what is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Well, Room 103's Mr Tamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}said that residents haven't been\Nsorting their rubbish properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}so he told us to pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}A lady got angry at me for that\Nin the rubbish collection area too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}She's probably in charge\Nof cleaning the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Miss Kinoshita, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- How do you know?\N- Because we talked for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}She is single,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and she said she liked\Nwatching musicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You really get along\Nwith everyone right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, not get along quickly,\Nyou get too familiar right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You dissed me a bit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, l didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sho, l am saying that this\Nis what people like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- You speak too loudly.\N- No, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sorry, we'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How about doing 50 more times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You're a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- That's enough!\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Good bye!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It's your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Write this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Write what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Write "It is your turn to kill."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Now.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}lt's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What's wrong, Mr Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What the heck?\Nl can't stand it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Mr Fujii?\N- l hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do l have to go\Nto every single flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Everyone is going to think\Nl'm a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:23:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Everyone is going to think\Nl'm a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Obviously something is wrong\Nwith me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Just calm down.\NLet's talk about it inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Well, let's talk here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- You don't want to?\N- l...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You don't want a weird guy\Nin your flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, that's not what l mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Kuzumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do you know a Masao Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Forget it if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Bhutanese Cuisine, Dorj's Diner{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't worry.\Nl guarantee that it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- It's hot!\N- But delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come on, give him some.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It's better to have a big bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What's the matter, Dorj?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What will you do\Non our next regular day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I see. I'm impressed\Nby how hard-working you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}By the way,\Nhave you fixed your DVD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why don't you come\Nand watch at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I couldn't fix it,\Nso l bought a Blu-ray player.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I spent a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I bought a cushion too!\NAn expensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why don't you come\Nand feel it at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I've got a cushion at home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come on, just come and feel it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You can come anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'll give you my spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.00,0:24:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.88,0:24:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But don't bring the friends\Nwho share the flat with you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.72,0:24:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Excuse me, do you mind\Nif l ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.36,0:24:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.16,0:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If you are Mr Masao Tanaka,\Nl might kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.43,0:24:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.91,0:24:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Tell me your name.\N- What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:24:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.73,0:25:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.53,0:25:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Sorry, l went to have dinner\Nwith Sanae.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.78,0:25:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I wondered if they knew him,\Nso l asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.63,0:25:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.75,0:25:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Even if they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.07,0:25:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}what were you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.54,0:25:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What will l do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.03,0:25:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Someone hates this Tanaka so much\Nthat they want to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.62,0:25:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}so l want to see what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.30,0:25:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Xinyi, do you know a Masao Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.62,0:25:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I have no Japanese friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The way you say that is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You're Chinese, why do you work\Nat a Bhutanese restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.78,0:25:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}There are Japanese people\Nworking at Italian restaurants too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.73,0:25:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}She's not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.73,0:26:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.05,0:26:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You're not thinking that you have\Nto kill someone this time, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.74,0:26:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.01,0:26:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We heard that you've been threatened\Nand we are worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It wasn't you guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.50,0:26:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.74,0:26:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The murderer who killed Yamagiwa\Nhas to be one of the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.17,0:26:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't trust anyone of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.46,0:26:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't want to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.06,0:26:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.14,0:26:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Did you buy those?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}There are various types nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.97,0:26:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why did you buy so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:26:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do l need to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.65,0:27:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}To make the world better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.65,0:27:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You didn't explain anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.13,0:27:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}There is an air of unrest\Nin the residential tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.86,0:27:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it has been causing suspicion\Nand fear in the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.02,0:27:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I can't let it pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.13,0:27:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Even so, why do you have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If it doesn't need me to do it,\Nthat means l can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It's sophism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.30,0:27:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I can foresee a bad outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.22,0:27:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l'm fed up with doing nothing\Nand letting it pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.66,0:27:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.62,0:27:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Just forget what happened\Nwhen you worked at the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.86,0:27:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}First, l'll get the whole picture\Nof what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.46,0:27:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Then, analyse it based on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.25,0:27:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}come up with ways to deal\Nwith the incident and solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.26,0:28:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Please go home.\N- No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- It's fine.\N- Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.21,0:28:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- What's going on?\N- l will go and buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I don't want to cause you trouble,\Nso l'll go myself from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.65,0:28:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We've been talking\Nabout what to eat for supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let her eat what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.94,0:28:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- No...\N- You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.70,0:28:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I wanted to have\Ndeep-fried meat cake
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.49,0:28:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and Misato prepared it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.98,0:28:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You shouldn't eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes. The doctor stressed that\Nl shouldn't eat anything deep-fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.58,0:28:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.06,0:28:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mum insisted on having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.10,0:28:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.86,0:28:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I was being childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.37,0:29:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}There are more and more things\Nl can't do when l grow old,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}so l say l want to eat this\Nor l want to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.06,0:29:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and use words\Nto take my mind off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.22,0:29:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But Misato takes\Nwhat l say seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.54,0:29:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}On top of that, she made a meat cake\Nas big as a sandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}When l saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.40,0:29:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it made me feel so sorry for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.44,0:29:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}that my health is too bad for me\Nto eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.17,0:29:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay, mum. lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do you enjoy making old people cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.24,0:29:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course l don't enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.06,0:29:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You should at least\Nmake it bite size.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.54,0:29:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}How can you make it like a scandal?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.18,0:29:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Or you can make soy pulp croquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}From this morning,\Nfor the whole day,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}your mother\Nhas been saying this nonstop,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.15,0:29:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}"Fried meat cake..."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.81,0:30:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}She has been chanting that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.13,0:30:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.05,0:30:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I thought l would do anything\Nto stop her meat cake chanting
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.12,0:30:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and l did my best\Nto make a huge meat cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.36,0:30:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Can you imagine just a bit\Nhow l felt at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't shout. lt's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.20,0:30:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sorry, l haven't done good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.92,0:30:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I will go and buy something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.88,0:30:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.44,0:30:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Nana, do you want to hang out\Nsomewhere this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.00,0:30:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We haven't been to anywhere\Nsince we moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.04,0:31:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Many things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.52,0:31:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.04,0:31:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Many things happened, that's exactly\Nwhy we should go out for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.48,0:31:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yeah. l'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.76,0:31:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}At least go to the city office,\Nthen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.04,0:31:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It's time to register our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I actually wanted you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sorry. l am not in the mood\Nto do that even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.36,0:31:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's do something\Nwe can do at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.32,0:31:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.98,0:31:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's have a bath together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.68,0:31:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That's what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.80,0:31:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.84,0:31:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- It's too sudden.\N- l suddenly want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.64,0:31:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why? You have been going out\Nevery night lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.96,0:32:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Not every night. Just twice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.92,0:32:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.56,0:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's fix a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.56,0:32:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I won't arrange anything\Non that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.92,0:32:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and l won't make myself too tired\Nduring the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.88,0:32:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But l don't mean\Nl want to do it so vigorously,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.16,0:32:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and l don't want to schedule it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.76,0:32:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We do that when our feelings\Nbond together,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.04,0:32:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}then our bodies bond together too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.72,0:32:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't say it like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'll satisfy my unfulfilled desire
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.90,0:32:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}by turning it\Ninto the desire for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.82,0:32:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Just look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.18,0:32:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Look closely\Nat how l eat the lettuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.20,0:32:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Look and think\Nthat l really love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.40,0:33:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.40,0:33:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.24,0:33:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.82,0:33:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.70,0:33:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, Ono. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.70,0:33:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.46,0:33:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.78,0:33:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Could you have expected\Nto have a present from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.94,0:33:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.74,0:33:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Ono, this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.80,0:34:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}They're sweet rice crackers.\Nl made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.82,0:34:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The rice, the oil and the syrup used\Nare all organic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.58,0:34:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You can make sweet rice crackers\Nyourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.06,0:34:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Tell me what you think next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.52,0:34:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.53,0:34:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Touo University Hospital{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.05,0:34:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Dr Yamagiwa's murderer\Nstill has not been caught{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.99,0:34:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Truth Weekly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.59,0:34:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.86,0:34:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}lt is your turn to kill.\NAttachment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.65,0:34:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Yamagiwa was my classmate\Nin college.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.41,0:35:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Yamagiwa was my classmate\Nin college.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.25,0:35:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}I've always hated him so much
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.09,0:35:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}that l wanted to pull his head off\Nmany times.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.85,0:35:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Someone recorded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.21,0:35:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}New email: lt is your turn to kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Attachment: Movie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.29,0:35:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hello, Mr Atsushi Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.33,0:35:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Does this look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.13,0:35:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It is your bath towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.05,0:35:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}On the towel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.29,0:35:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}your DNA and Yutaro Yamagiwa's DNA\Nwill be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This and the voice recording\Nsent to you just now
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.85,0:35:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}will confirm\Nthat you are the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.76,0:35:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.20,0:35:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But if you obey the rule\Nand do what you should,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.01,0:36:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l will take the responsibility\Nand dispose both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.61,0:36:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}lt is your turn to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.61,0:36:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Of course it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.17,0:36:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.13,0:36:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l don't even know where the guy\Nl'm supposed to kill is!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.21,0:36:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The patient is waiting.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.09,0:36:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Shut up! l am coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.89,0:36:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}This guys is hopeless.\Nl want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'll call the next patient in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.45,0:36:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.89,0:36:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Number 214, Mr Tanaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.89,0:36:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Masao Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.17,0:36:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.85,0:36:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Masao?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.53,0:36:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.26,0:37:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Number 214, Mr Tanaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.26,0:37:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Masao Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.58,0:37:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.26,0:37:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Masao?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.74,0:37:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.53,0:37:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, my? You are a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.74,0:37:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The Bhutanese diner's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.70,0:37:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l am the owner, Dorj. Cheers, mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.94,0:37:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.86,0:37:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But Tanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.14,0:37:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Oh, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.14,0:37:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Actually, l am not Dorj.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.82,0:38:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If a Bhutanese restaurant is run\Nby an Osaka guy with a thick accent,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.78,0:38:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}it won't be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.14,0:38:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That's why l pretended to be\Na Bhutanese guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.01,0:38:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Like, "Welcome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That means you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Masao Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.90,0:38:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.30,0:38:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Bhutanese Cuisine, Dorj's Diner{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.60,0:38:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l will go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.85,0:38:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You'll go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.29,0:39:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.69,0:39:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come on, come and watch a DVD\Nat my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I'm going to meet someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.98,0:39:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}With your friend\Nwho is staying illegally?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.30,0:39:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}If you don't want me to tell\Nthe police about your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.66,0:39:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}come and watch a DVD at my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.14,0:39:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hey, this is nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.78,0:39:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am not nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.14,0:39:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I only want to watch a DVD with you\Non my fluffy cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.18,0:39:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.90,0:39:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Slow and steady wins the case,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}I am home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.03,0:41:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You went on a date again?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.94,0:41:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We just met up after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.98,0:41:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We had dinner, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.78,0:41:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You can invite me occasionally too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.69,0:41:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Can we change the topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.21,0:41:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.57,0:41:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Do you know Room 403's Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.70,0:41:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What about Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.70,0:42:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Fujii came and asked me whether you\Nand the diner's owner were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.28,0:42:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What time did he come?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.77,0:42:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The owner of the number you dialled\Ncannot answer your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.57,0:42:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Please leave a message\Nafter the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.79,0:42:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sir! Mr Dorj!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.67,0:42:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.63,0:42:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Sir! Mr Dorj!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.79,0:42:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka! Masao Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.43,0:42:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.43,0:42:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why? Xinyi, you sound desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.91,0:42:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.47,0:42:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am alive. l am very alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.73,0:42:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.09,0:42:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Are you alone in the diner?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.41,0:42:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.85,0:42:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why? Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.73,0:42:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You should go home right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.09,0:42:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Should l?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.78,0:42:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Will you come to my home?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.34,0:43:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}You should have taken my spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.06,0:43:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}But now your friend is safe,\Neveryone is happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.74,0:43:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.50,0:43:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}It doesn't matter,\Nyou're totally my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.06,0:43:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What can l do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.42,0:43:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Xinyi, you lit up my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Manager: Murder? Suicide?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.41,0:43:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Yamagiwa: Killed by the one\Nwho wants the manager dead?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.41,0:43:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Masao Tanaka: Will Fujii kill him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.61,0:43:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Nana, let's do\Ncore training together!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.05,0:45:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Xinyi. Xinyi, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.01,0:45:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Come. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.50,0:45:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.58,0:45:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.58,0:45:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- What is it?\N- Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.02,0:45:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.53,0:45:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}It is your turn to kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.37,0:45:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Your Turn to Kill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.49,0:45:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Your wife didn't tell you\Nabout the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.25,0:45:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}Shota found out his wife's lie{\i0}\NDid she lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.13,0:45:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Maybe she wrote your name, Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.01,0:45:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx346\fscy397}There is another murder--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.21,0:46:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l just heard a loud noise.
